(41, 1, 'Hey there!!', 1506370999, '235663883628189', 64, 1055, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(42, 1, 'Feel free to zoom in and out to see the screen better.\n', 1506371164, '235663883628189', 64, 1055, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(43, 1, 'Welcome to the space! Please share your name and where youre from as you enter :)', 1506371377, '235663883628189', 64, 1055, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(44, 1, 'whats happening\n', 1506372463, '10209160242101050', 1, 1066, 'Matt Ready'),
(45, 1, 'Thanks for creating this software Matt! Were excited to be able to attend the Mandala Legislative Theatre!', 1506385994, '1408199662568390', 66, 1069, 'Sarah Rohr'),
(46, 1, 'Starting soon\n', 1506388826, '10209160242101050', 1, 1069, 'Matt Ready'),
(47, 1, 'Will the video appear or is there steps I take to turn it on?', 1506389428, '1408199662568390', 66, 1071, 'Sarah Rohr'),
(48, 1, 'It will appear', 1506389470, '10209160242101050', 1, 1071, 'Matt Ready'),
(49, 1080, 'Welcome to the LGBTQ Youth Theatre conversation!', 1506389633, '235663883628189', 64, 1069, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(50, 1, 'Reload the page and you should see the video load :)\n', 1506389866, '10209160242101050', 1, 1071, 'Matt Ready'),
(51, 1, 'Welcome everyone to the theatre! Marc is up there explaining Legislative Theatre now. The Brazilian revolutionary Boals modality.', 1506390603, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(52, 1, 'Thank you for the welcome. Good to be here tonight.\n ', 1506391040, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(53, 1, 'You have some guests from Alaska!\n', 1506391075, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(54, 1, 'Where is everyone here from?', 1506391098, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(55, 1, 'Oh hi Sara from Alaska!!', 1506391115, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(56, 1, 'HI!!', 1506391142, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(57, 1, 'Im in Columbia, MO.\n', 1506391158, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(58, 1, 'Have to say... Im proud of the bathroom signs here ;) \"All Genders\". We are challenging our community to take these steps forward.\n', 1506391292, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(59, 1, 'Hi Simona from MO!', 1506391314, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(60, 1, 'I hope everyone is unmuted for this amazing song by Liv and the youth performers!', 1506391386, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(61, 1, 'Hi!\n', 1506391560, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(62, 1, 'Powerful play. Hope everyone can see it ok', 1506392074, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(63, 1, 'er... this last scene was painful and powerful to see. wow.', 1506392222, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(64, 1, 'Agreed Simona... your answer to the question I think was expressed in the play as well.', 1506392296, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(65, 1, 'Any questions about the rules of forum so far?', 1506392587, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(66, 1, 'Time for the forum to begin!', 1506392812, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(67, 1, 'I want to discuss Sarahs answer... I wonder if walking out would put Kevin at risk for getting in trouble and make school more challenging for him? A personal experience of mine. What do you think?', 1506393691, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(68, 1, 'Walking out and going to a trusted ally - teacher, counselor, etc. Maybe then Kevin wouldnt face the same possibility of getting in trouble.', 1506393898, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(69, 1, 'And wouldnt be facing this alone.', 1506393923, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(70, 1, 'So it sounds like by having an ally in school that all students are aware about, it would be a safe way for trans students to have a back up. I know that would have helped me in that situation.', 1506394028, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(71, 1, 'One step in that would be ensuring an ally always be available and known to students... which I know is not the case for many middle and high schools. Any other ideas?', 1506394223, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(72, 1, 'Will you write that as a proposal Sarafina?', 1506394234, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(73, 1, 'Yes I will mention this conversation and write it as a proposal. Good idea!', 1506394280, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(74, 1, 'Of course, its possible/likely that there is already a policy for something like that, but its not enacted.', 1506394304, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(75, 1, 'Yeah, its hard to find an ally on ones own. I think it helps if you are an ally and have some privilege/power, then its important to be aware of your positionality, and then make it known somehow that you are an ally. And then take that action if called u', 1506394325, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(76, 1, '...called upon to be a supportive ally.', 1506394368, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(77, 1, 'True. I will push for this to be heard by the folks here tonight. It will always be on our records on this site to use for future work and proposals. Loving these ideas.', 1506394460, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(78, 1, 'Ok well be on break for ten minutes', 1506395049, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(79, 1, 'Policy suggestion for School Board- add LGBTQ education to K-12 curriculum.', 1506395268, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(80, 1, 'Also- add policy for hospital regarding LGBTQ education for all employees.', 1506395316, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(81, 1, 'Yes great ideas Sarah. I will write that down.', 1506395404, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(82, 1, 'OK we are about ready to take remote votes everyone!!', 1506395756, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(83, 1, 'how do we vote?', 1506395790, '10100313741326838', 67, 1072, 'Sarah Finnell'),
(84, 1, 'on the left i will write the policy suggestion and you can vote up or down', 1506395855, '235663883628189', 64, 1071, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(85, 1, 'Up Vote the policy in the Voting window on the left if you wish to vote.', 1506396254, '10209160242101050', 1, 1077, 'Matt Ready'),
(86, 1, 'Up vote or down vote', 1506396273, '10209160242101050', 1, 1077, 'Matt Ready'),
(87, 1, 'Interesting about all counselors being trained for LGBTQ... thoughts? I feel that is unrealistic.', 1506396638, '235663883628189', 64, 1077, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(88, 1, 'in other words i feel there needs to be someone designated specifically.', 1506396721, '235663883628189', 64, 1077, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(89, 1, 'It may seem unrealistic. I hear you. Still, I think that having as many people ready to respond to any need from an LGBTQ+ student should be a priority... in order to ensure that there are multiple points of entry for young people to get help.', 1506398209, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(90, 1, '\"fire all liberal teachers who give students a hard time and/or lower their grades just because they dont agree with student politics.\" from Al joining from FB\n', 1506398750, '235663883628189', 64, 1077, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(91, 1, 'centering and valuing voices', 1506398758, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(92, 1, 'faith in community', 1506398789, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(93, 1, 'Sorry I got your comment a little too late Simona I will try to share in the open after the sculpture. Beautiful', 1506398811, '235663883628189', 64, 1077, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(94, 1, 'OK THANKS EVERYONE! COME BACK TOMORROW NIGHT!!', 1506398929, '235663883628189', 64, 1077, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(95, 1, 'Thank you for facilitating the online work!', 1506399051, '10154738596241510', 69, 1073, 'Simona Perales Simkins'),
(96, 1, 'Hi is everyone seeing the video ok? Excited for tonight we have a big crowd show up.', 1506476805, '235663883628189', 64, 1086, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(97, 1, 'What a talented young person!!! Beautiful song.', 1506477250, '1408199662568390', 66, 1077, 'Sarah Rohr'),
(98, 1, 'Amazing talented and brave young folks', 1506477687, '235663883628189', 64, 1086, 'Sarafina Landis'),
(99, 1, 'Can you hear ok? That was powerful.', 1506479116, '235663883628189', 64, 1086, 'Sarafina Landis'),
